There are million tokens in the pool. 
Each depositor can withdraw his tokens starting 7 days from the day of the deposit.
When the tokens are deposited, the calculation is like this:
the amount of tokens deposited *100 / the amount of tokens in the pool after the deposit.
For example: Nitai deposited 300000 tokens in a pool that contained a million tokens. 
After 7 days from the day of the deposit, Nitai will be able to withdraw 23.0769230769% of the pool.

 